吴某光系累犯，建议对被告吴某光判处二年六个月有期徒刑。（来源：澎湃新闻） 孙海洋：孙卓被拐案将于 4 月 7 日开庭，希望严惩人贩子"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-11046efa50c82652eb0b5fb125eca1d2_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "11 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/593344651"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Isa62gO+2pKF4EAMaCDk0MTM2MDMwIL7cpKEGMAE4SkAXcgk1OTMzNDQ2NTF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "24_1680568775.4317536", "card_id": "Q_593280450", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 43}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么 14 寸笔记本普遍不带网口？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "连游戏本都不带，一味的追求薄的意义在哪里？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-4034e3cb65e627a52c31b9616c3e2850_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "11 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/593280450"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Isa62gO+2pKF4EAMaCDk0MTIxNzI0IMnwoaEGMAU4TUAYcgk1OTMyODA0NTB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "25_1680568775.4325604", "card_id": "Q_548850146", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 174}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "各个车企热衷于「大彩电」风潮，跟风多屏设计是否有必要？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "现在汽车中控屏越来越大，理想 one 的三联屏到 L9 的前后三块大屏，EQS 则直接把 1.41 米的大长屏摆在了中控台上，飞凡 R7 的三联屏尺寸甚至高达 43 英寸，很多车企造车都在呈现大屏多屏趋势，然而有人觉得屏幕的数量和尺寸并不重要，重要的是体验和背后的系统优化，但也有人觉得大屏能提升整车的档次，感觉内饰更有科技感，大家觉得汽车屏幕又大又多才好么？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-5a99bdc86a6e344e3d38fad49fb6847f_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "11 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/5488